		id

		displayName
		frontEnvironment
		frontVersion
		backEnvironment
		backVersion
		subject
		description
		attachments
		screenRecording
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	supportFindIssue (query: $query)
	{
		id
		rowId
		externalId
		externalStatus
		externalColorStatus

		displayName

		frontVersion
		backEnvironment

		description
		attachments
		screenRecording
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt

}

		meta

		updatedAt

}
